description: Checks whether the container registry name is available for use. The name must contain only alphanumeric characters, be globally unique, and between 5 and 50 characters in length.

registry_name_check_request.description: The object containing information for the availability request.

message.description: If any, the error message that provides more detail for the reason that the name is not available.

nameavailable.description: The value that indicates whether the name is available.

reason.description: If any, the reason that the name is not available.
